comments: Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Jokic (DEN) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) layup attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Lowry (MIA) engage and immediately disengage as marginal arm contact occurs while the rebound goes overhead.
Murray (DEN) and Lowry (MIA) briefly engage and disengage with one another while on the perimeter during the pick.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) brushes and makes marginal contact with Robinson's (MIA) left leg while contesting the jump shot attempt.
Brown (DEN) and Martin (MIA) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Vincent (MIA) straddles the lane line and moves to imminently guard Jokic (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) and Vincent (MIA) mutually engage during the rebound and marginal contact occurs as Vincent loses his balance.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Adebayo (MIA) and is not in a legal guarding position as contact occurs during Adebayo's upward shooting motion.
Jokic (DEN) moves towards the basket and does not deliver any illegal contact to Vincent (MIA) on the play.
Butler (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Vincent (MIA) brushes Jokic's (DEN) left shoulder and marginal contact occurs as he defends Jokic's post shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) turns to roll and incidental contact occurs with Gordon (DEN) as he goes under the pick.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
